  "title": "今日开源（2025-12-11）：阿里开源 Wan-Move，点级精细运动控制，赋能图像到视频模型高效升级",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500852&idx=1&sn=25c9e7d010062a6549f5f6adfcba678b",
  "date": "2025-12-11 09:48:00",
