  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Wan-Move</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"666\" data-imgfileid=\"100017186\" data-ratio=\"0.5712962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9cb5c3c3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwEhIQH7XnxgPibk6sOvOUXeoRE8oRS8yFHlzsydiaNZhs9f0GbL3kZ57otB0Z1sfMAHWgLYw9YBiblQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Wan-Move是一个用于视频生成的简单且可扩展的运动控制框架。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">潜在轨迹引导</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">实现了精细的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">点级运动控制</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，能够生成5秒钟、480p分辨率的视频，运动控制能力达到商业系统的水平。Wan-Move可以无缝集成到现有的图像到视频模型中，无需改变架构或添加额外的运动模块。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/wan-move\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/wan-move</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：Nanbeige4</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"724\" data-imgfileid=\"100017185\" data-ratio=\"0.6212962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17efd350&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwEhIQH7XnxgPibk6sOvOUXewr3uC915EtUm6TF10nTVHfQ2RK2uqBJmtSGg0kR4XpDsbicCMuSRy6A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Nanbeige4-3B-Thinking通过先进的知识蒸馏技术和针对性的强化学习优化，显著提升了模型的推理能力，在多种具有挑战性的基准测试中表现出色。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该版本在32B参数以下的开放模型中，在AIME、GPQA-Diamond、Arena-Hard-V2和BFCL-V4上建立了新的最先进（SOTA）结果，标志着在紧凑规模下提供强大而高效的推理能力的重大里程碑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nanbeige4\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nanbeige4</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：Lightning</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"576\" data-imgfileid=\"100017187\" data-ratio=\"0.49444444444444446\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ebc15307&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwEhIQH7XnxgPibk6sOvOUXekDnXnC44MXOGQeojUriceNwtdMicJXzHXfiaFtHK4VhKla8rwSfA8e2TA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Lightning-1.7B 是一款高效的实用模型，专为边缘计算和低延迟工作流程设计。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">Lightning-1.7B 在逻辑、问答和编码方面的能力有所提升，其真正的优势在于</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">增强的创造力和实用功能</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。它被设计为一个理想的“伴随”模型，足够小以在设备上运行，且对内存影响最小，但足够智能以处理复杂的元数据生成任务。</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型基于强大的 Qwen3-1.7B 基础模型，并在 NousResearch Hermes-3 数据集上进行了微调。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lightning\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lightning</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：ODB-dLLM</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4425925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"514\" data-imgfileid=\"100017189\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4a80cc13&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwEhIQH7XnxgPibk6sOvOUXeLLLusnKIPejOw5xrQbusZibo28F3LKjYRMuHia7zhHPrGkFCtpqI8fsA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★ODB-dLLM是一个旨在加速扩散语言模型的框架。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">通过分析现有dLLM推理框架中的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">计算和内存绑定阶段</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，ODB-dLLM引入了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">自适应长度预测策略</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">跳跃共享推测解码</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，以优化硬件平台上的计算-内存特性，从而最大化推</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">理效率</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/odb-dllm\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/odb-dllm</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：LoVoRA</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6212962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"722\" data-imgfileid=\"100017190\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6204967e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwEhIQH7XnxgPibk6sOvOUXebtvejY8X1pibD6pzKzA53G9rNemyViao4fPruibPhSPmccHm9QlJRbqvA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LoVoRA是一个创新的框架，旨在实现文本引导的无掩码视频对象移除和添加</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。该项目无需在推理时使用辅助掩码或参考图像，能够在保持高空间精度和强时空一致性的同时，自动学习密集的时空编辑区域。LoVoRA结合了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">可学习的对象感知定位机制</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">扩散掩码预测器</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，仅通过文本提示和原始视频即可进行端到端的视频编辑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lovora\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lovora</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：SimScale</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1787037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"208\" data-imgfileid=\"100017191\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7c7b93f7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwEhIQH7XnxgPibk6sOvOUXeRyoNbghibZMh2hFgmKvkUMQaFsGGGmc4tA2A8dFMrqmTibTEaen7ewBQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★SimScale项目旨在通过大规模的真实世界模拟学习驾驶。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目开发了一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">可扩展的模拟管道</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，能够合成多样化且高保真的反应性驾驶场景，并提供伪专家演示。通过有效的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">仿真-现实协同</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">训练策略，项目在各种端到端规划器中提高了鲁棒性和泛化能力。此外，项目还揭示了仿真-现实学习系统在端到端自动驾驶中的扩展特性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/simscale\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/simscale</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总并简要介绍了六个最新的 AI 项目，涵盖了视频生成、大模型推理、边缘部署、扩散模型优化、视频编辑以及自动驾驶模拟等多个前沿技术方向。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文汇总并简要介绍了六个最新的 AI 项目，涵盖了视频生成、大模型推理、边缘部署、扩散模型优化、视频编辑以及自动驾驶模拟等多个前沿技术方向。",
